            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once lightly browned, remove the tray[s] from the oven and push the wedges to one side</p><p>Add the <strong>browned arayes</strong> to the other side and return the tray[s] to the oven for 12-14 min or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your<strong> Lebanese-style beef arayes</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
