        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, bash your <strong>cucumber </strong>with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> and chop it into large, bite-sized pieces – this is your<strong> smashed cucumber</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>smashed cucumber </strong>with the<strong> remaining grated garlic </strong>(not a big garlic fan? Try using less!),<strong> sliced shallot </strong>and <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> cucumber yoghurt salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
