    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Lebanese-style beef arayes</strong> with the<strong> wedges</strong> and <strong>cucumber yoghurt salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved parsley</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
